title: Kodiak J-250 29 in. D-Handle Round Point Shovel
description: The Jackson J-250 D-Handle Round Point Shovel with a Closed Back has an extended blade socket that provides more steel for greater strength. Closed back design prevents mud and dirt build-up. Exclusive D-grip encases the wood completely to prevent twisting, cannot come loose. 30 in. seal-coated premium northern ash handles for strength and durability. Extra thick 14-gauge steel blade for maximum toughness.
